{"tid":1592590,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"FB流傳割席宣言~~~","createTime":"2019-09-24T16:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T14:56:59.000Z","uid":269526,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"353346522ef0a622d61b91c7713ee82eed40ebe7","tid":1592590,"uid":269526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"手轉動<br />\n<br />\n連登仔最新《割席宣言》<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於港共同狗隻對香港人既打壓無效<br />\n極有可能出現偽裝示威者以抺黑示威者之行為<br />\n因此<br />\n現正作出割蓆宣言<br />\n<br />\n一，示威者不會惡意傷害任何無辜人士之性命財產。<br />\n二，示威者不強姦，不搶劫。<br />\n三，示威者對報導事實的記者，醫護，外國朋友等一律表示尊重。<br />\n四，示威者作出的一切行為皆對準港共極權或任何助長港共極權之人士、團體和機構。<br />\n五，不會持有鎖匙開警車車尾箱。<br />\n六，不會有警車車匙揸警車。<br />\n七，不會持有同警慌同款伸縮警棍。<br />\n八，不會搶槍如此不智讓警慌為開實彈而舖路。<br />\n<br />\n註：<br />\n無辜人士例子：路過市民，遊客。<br />\n未FC"},{"pid":"da2d667694c9312849a07314dbe40efc5fe48119","tid":1592590,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"0b50bf280b8837d30ec9642bb19fe416ba3ef6b6","tid":1592590,"uid":269526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QfkOTzv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQfkOTzv.jpg&h=e29149f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b02c7060680bf16643929bca522855703168e167","tid":1592590,"uid":269526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c990KGq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc990KGq.jpg&h=3857bdf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c095b9761369beaaab4af07636051ec2f78fc70","tid":1592590,"uid":43715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"353